{"tid":2044752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳中學師生聯署聲明　教聯會譴責將學校拖入政治漩渦","createTime":"2020-05-31T10:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T16:17:25.000Z","uid":66324,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3bc1c5d5163b4a35e5a09a6026feb3cb9797475f","tid":2044752,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529413-20200531.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529413-20200531.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=191167ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529413-20200531.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bd8f2c9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529413-20200531.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-05-31 HKT 17:38<br />\n<br />\n教聯會批評，網上出現多個自稱是中學師生校友發起的聯署，反對「港區國安法」，擅用師生名義作政治表態，將學校拖入反對國家的政治漩渦之中，干擾學校正常運作，予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n教聯會指，有人故技重施企圖騎劫學校，呼籲辦學團體、法團校董會在大是大非面前，果斷劃清界線，切割反對國家的行為。<br />\n<br />\n在社交網絡群組，流傳多間中學的師生及校友發起聯署聲明，反對「港區國安法」及反對立法破壞「一國兩制」，涉及學校數目至今超過30間。亦有學校反對《國歌法》，憂慮會為香港帶來更多政治打壓，侵蝕香港的自由及法治等。"},{"pid":"96ef53ed63b1984af9b6a805af20a04c8a08e6ea","tid":2044752,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda9b85d715143f5bafa375e7b3b47dfcf145758","tid":2044752,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"你又叫Ｄ後生簽名，on 9"},{"pid":"04c619f7573287ac29dcf82516409243d848c484","tid":2044752,"uid":72457,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"教拹根本就係毒瘤<br />